===Intransitive verb===
{{en-verb|divid|ing}}

# To separate into two or more parts.
# (''biology'') Of a cell, to [[reproduce]] by dividing.
# (''arithmetic'') To be a [[factor]] of.
#:''3 '''divides''' 6.''

